data.description: VA ASSUMABLE LOAN! Practically new Chesmar home located in sought after Stone Creek! Don't miss out on the chance to own one of the only LAKETON floor plans in the neighborhood! This home boasts an open floor-plan, vaulted ceilings that open to second level, and a gorgeous floor to ceiling custom electric fireplace in living. Beautiful glass panoramic sliding doors allow for tons of natural light and unrestricted views of the backyard. Stunning gourmet kitchen offers ample cabinets, countertop space and a large over-sized island. Gas cooktop in kitchen. Additional bedroom and en-suite bath located on first floor making the perfect mother-in-law suite! Spacious primary bedroom with en-suite bath offers dual sinks, soaking tub, shower and a large walk-in closet. Upstairs you'll find the 3 remaining bedrooms, media room, and game room-loft space. Cozy outdoor fireplace located on back patio. TWO tankless hot water heaters. Walking distance to elementary school, community pool and parks!
